# 统一各类文件的换行符，避免在 Windows/Mac 之间来回改动导致 git 误判"本地已修改"、拉不到代码。
* text=auto eol=lf

# Windows 批处理必须 CRLF
*.bat text eol=crlf
*.cmd text eol=crlf
*.ps1 text eol=crlf

# Mac 脚本用 LF
*.command text eol=lf
*.sh text eol=lf

# 二进制文件不做任何换行转换
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.icns binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
